<holidayType guid="8e8285ae-c1fd-4f2c-8c60-e1236e2300d9" id="24076" nodeName="Switzerland Half Price Travel Card and Free Rucksack" isDoc="" updated="2022-05-25T13:33:20.7670000Z" parentGUID="e65cbae5-17c8-4dcc-a98e-cbd6e7154c59" nodeTypeAlias="holidayType" templateAlias="HolidayType" sortOrder="16" published="false" isBlueprint="false">
  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<p><img src="/media/13064814/walkers-rucksack-switzerland.jpg" alt="Swiss" rel="858,410" /></p>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>Inghams has a wide range of destinations for you to choose from on Switzerland holidays, plus an enthralling selection of scenic tours, by rail and/or lake steamer.  We also offer the chance to travel by rail all the way from the UK to our hotels in Switzerland.</p>
<p>Highlights of holidays in Switzerland include trips to see world-famous peaks, such as the magnificent Matterhorn, the Jungfrau and the Eiger, and relaxing lake cruises on one of the many lakes. From <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> to <a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3}" title="Wengen">Wengen</a>, from <a data-udi="umb://document/527f062dda374fee961e7ca5209c3d26" href="/{localLink:umb://document/527f062dda374fee961e7ca5209c3d26}" title="Davos">Davos</a> to <a data-udi="umb://document/10d1327258a9451090acfa272ea0be1f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/10d1327258a9451090acfa272ea0be1f}" title="Lugano">Lugano</a>, from <strong>Lake Geneva</strong> to <a data-udi="umb://document/70b1a325037e4112bc5e6feeb41d725f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/70b1a325037e4112bc5e6feeb41d725f}" title="Lake Lucerne">L;alake Lucerne</a> and from <a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a> to <a data-udi="umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e}" title="Saas Fee">Saas Fee</a> – there is plenty to see and do. <br /><br />A <strong>Swiss Half-Price Travel Card worth over £80</strong> is included for all guests booking an Inghams holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>!  This free card entitles you to 50% reduction on first and second class travel on most of the superb Swiss transport network (trains, cable-cars, boats, buses etc) - a great value way to explore and experience Switzerland’s amazing scenery. It also gives free travel to children from 6 to 15 years old, when accompanied by a parent or grandparent with the Family or Grandparent card.</p>
<p><strong>Whether hiking in the mountains or strolling by the lakes, a good quality rucksack is essential and we’re offering all our guests booking their Switzerland summer 2016 holiday <strong>a <span style="color: red;">FREE</span> walkers’ rucksack per couple,</strong> while stocks last!</strong></p>
<p>It has 22 litres capacity and a wealth of useful features including padded adjustable shoulder, a breathable mesh back-panel, mesh side-pockets for your water bottle and even an attachment point for your walking poles. And its dimensions are well within our airlines’ hand baggage regulations.</p>
<p>Rucksacks will be sent out by our appointed independent distributor (Colourgraphics). <strong>To claim your free rucksack</strong>, simply email <a href="mailto:rucksack@colourgraphic-arts.co.uk">rucksack@colourgraphic-arts.co.uk</a> (or ask your travel agent to email for you), providing your <strong>booking reference, lead name and required postal delivery address</strong>.</p>
<p>If you do not have email access, please call John Scardarella on 01428 772 230.</p>
<p>See <a href="/{localLink:66d6dfd2-b127-48e8-b6d8-228d6e59ea65}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms and conditions</a> for further details. <strong>Free Rucksack Offer:</strong> All name &amp; address information supplied to the distributor in conjunction with this promotion will be destroyed after despatch and will not be used for any future marketing activity by them or by Inghams. Guests’ addresses supplied to them by travel agents will not be passed to Inghams at any time.</p>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
